    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "New host and distribution records for Buprestidae (Coleoptera) from the state of Morelos, Mexico" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4475175>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4475177> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4475175>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–8. Dorsal habitus of: 1) Acmaeodera aquila Nelson 1994. 2) A. marginarcuata Westcott 1998. 3) Tetragonoschema humerale Waterhouse 1882. 4) Agrilus albovariegatus Hespenheide 1990. 5) A. angustus Chevrolat 1835. 6) A. griseoniger Hespenheide 1990. 7) A. ruginosus Waterhouse 1890. 8) A. tejupilcoensis Fisher 1933. Scale bars = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4475175/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4475177>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–15. Dorsal habitus of: 9) Agrilus verityi Hespenheide 1990. 10) Brachys intervallorum Hespenheide 1990. 11) Leiopleura balloui Fisher 1938. 12) Lius cuneiformis Fisher 1922. 13) L. hintoni Fisher 1933. 14) L. mexicanus Fisher 1922. 15) Pachyschelus pubicollis Waterhouse 1889. Scale bars = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4475177/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

